FORMER company boss Brent Morrison has been named student of the year by Ayrshire College. Student of year award for ex-boss FORMER company boss Brent Morrison has been named student of the year by Ayrshire College.The 54-year-old ex-businessman, from Ayr, graduated in HND Art and Design and one of his college paintings now hangs in the Robert Burns Birthplace Museum in Alloway.College principal Heather Dunk said Brent closed his firm during the recession but added: &quot;I am &shy;delighted that Brent &shy;applied his business acumen and artistic ability to his studies.&quot; 